---
title: Rosemary Fig Pork Tenderloin with Kale & Sweet Potato Jumble
description: Figs are one of the best things about Autumn and our chefs have found using fig jam in this recipe, cooked down with rosemary and butter, makes a rich, sweet sauce that perfectly compliments the meat—a juicy, pan-seared, then roasted, pork tenderloin. Pair that with earthy roasted sweet potatoes, red onion, and sauteed kale for a hearty and colorful plate; a perfect dinner idea for a chilly night in.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/rosemary-fig-pork-tenderloin-7e629dba.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/rosemary-fig-pork-tenderloin-6398e03d2c92a379770cd43c-28565264.pdf
